reviewText:
This DVD did not work.  I would like a replacement.  The other DVD I purchased worked fine but this one didn't work.

Thank you.

When I first heard about this story I couldn't believe it happened.  I have read and I recommend the books on this topic. After seeing this DVD I finally understood why there was doubt about her story from the beginning.  I do recommend this DVD.
